save_all_item_states

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
save_all_item_states -  This method saves the mapping of state/location  information for items owned by a player to disk.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int save_all_item_states(mixed pl_name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^pl_name%^RESET%^ -   player object or name
%^BOLD%^item%^RESET%^ -      item object or identifier
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if successful
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/item_tracker.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method saves the mapping of state/location 
information for items owned by a player to disk.
.EP

